{
  "id": "RAW_4834d4",
  "title": "实测可灵 AI 的新视频模型，它生成的动作戏酷到封神。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647675298&idx=1&sn=9da49588ea9750e9f4fad9f814274261",
  "date": "2025-09-22 01:31:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可灵2.5，来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><font size=\"3\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅已经对可灵的超级创作者们正式进行灰度内测，还在这个周末，登上了釜山国际电影节。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191522\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33568904593639576\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"566\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"566\" data-backh=\"190\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd0b628f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURr3rZmlq5OdgbQR3g4Vl74nibTHN6NlWiboY8nsFm0WLxdQxMA34IpYHA3QGic7k0UT0wicbxEXoN0Npg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我其实已经很久很久没做过小片子了，在前几天拿到可灵2.5的体验资格以后，试了一下，居然，又激起了我的一些创作欲望。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就，我自己是非常喜欢科幻、非常喜欢动作、也非常喜欢一些张力很足的动作戏的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些，是过往几乎所有的AI视频模型，都不太行的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但，可灵2.5，不说媲美那种动作大片，但是，还是把AI视频在动作和表演上，又拉到了一个新的高度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我也花了一整天的时间，用可灵2.5，手搓了一个AI版《速度与激情》，做了一个小片子，更直观的感受一下，可灵2.5在动作戏上的实力。</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里面可以说是集齐了我从十五岁到现在喜欢的所有视觉效果，肾上腺素飙升的追车战，经费燃烧的爆炸大场面，拳拳到肉的打戏，超级酷炫的漂移，等等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这些效果，现在，可灵能以一己之力，给我都实现了，如果在24年，这就是不可能想象的。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从这个小片子，大家应该就能感受到，可灵2.5的能力圈了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我把他总结成两块：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">运动的超进化，表演的超进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">一块一块来说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一.</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">运动的超进化</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先用一个case，让你们直观感受一下可灵2.5的进步到底有多大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：电影大片风格，一个身穿黑衣，头戴面具的金发女特工破窗而出，借助升降绳迅速滑落在地，然后飞速跑到准备好的摩托车旁，镜头跟随女特工运动。然后女特工跨上摩托车，在街道上飞驰，周围的景物因高速运动而动态模糊，采用令人眩晕的高速镜头，低机位拍摄，突出女特工的速度感和力量感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可灵2.5，非常丝滑地衔接了下落、奔跑、骑摩托几个动作，最后飞驰而去。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还顾及到了破窗时玻璃渣散落，落地时蹲一下缓冲，这种极具真实感的细节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个看下来真的很爽。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191576\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df449e21&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOEsI1tDA3yfrPVoGaPGeEkN3Ika9Ram6d19ruZib3jmzNCoN9V4pkyrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而可灵2.1，只能保持人物基本不崩坏，但所有与环境交互的细节，全都糊掉了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下降到一半绳子不知所踪，说好的高空速降变成了一楼跳窗，摩托车凭空出现在大马路上，跨上摩托的动作也是错的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191614\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c6c9579&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOsKwTFCXNMYMBdriaqvG66QACs7UdmDArMPQZonSTOIsZsKgm6rqfFDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再来看一个栗子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：霓虹都市背景，车辆爆炸，火光四起，黑衣特工从车中飞跃而出，翻滚落地，然后迅速爬起，左手右手同时举枪开火，镜头跟随特工运动，最后环绕特工360度旋转。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可灵2.5就一个字，稳。人物的动作稳，运镜也稳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191582\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e8383be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOqf9QjNpTIF3t5Gml0p8YasHHnibQWc1oYA0hc2uAuJzf0JUFzqsrPJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而可灵2.1看起来，就有种很忙、但不知在忙什么的感觉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"500191615\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9cfea053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQO171KboIiabUl38PjoNXQvcY8ibnQIZybSKaLM0FcW4DcWHcaOJAuMjvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再来看一个跑酷的case。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：镜头高速跟随，一个机甲在霓虹闪烁的赛博都市楼顶跑酷，灵活翻越金属栏杆，在大楼之间跨越，动作迅捷流畅。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可灵2.5的机器人跑酷过程中的动作和交互，相当真实。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至完全不需要做首尾帧，只要输入提示词，它就可以自动给你补全所有运动画面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">直接靠文生视频能达到这样的效果，我真的跪了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191577\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de0d8036&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOGxn9LK52dzt6UQs33Fjaw3p3ISC9Ct8QFHicicGZuRboUAWYG7212ibQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这是可灵2.1，会不受重力控制地，逐渐飞天。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191616\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfeeeeba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOJ61kgsLeZxE8ojTQ2BgA8U6cEx3F8ia9ibs4ZYsQN0yibOAjs0H9umZIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这么看下来，你们应该知道，可灵2.5的运动能力相比2.1到底提升多少了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再来欣赏几个可灵2.5跑出来的case。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我真的很喜欢这个跑酷的感觉，机器人动作和镜头运动配合得特别好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191583\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2cb0a8be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOLCHcFGcsqo0pcnUTu4tcGjbSzQo3zzxkC4xlpciac6bTBVVNzlGnP4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有这个第一视角跟随镜头，我在提示词里让它猛然加速，它真的做出了那种急迫感。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：他跨上最后一级台阶冲出地铁口，逆光里捕到前方那道模糊人影正要拐走，他猛地加速追过去，镜头跟随。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191584\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5598591549295775\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c8706a63&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOiaZ9BBJ5Nk9lsVUEre6xhqUQHkVJjZBibYhvxibquutLiaygkKvkh5Bp4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让可灵2.5生成各种运动镜头，效果也贼好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让它滑雪，它给你来套空翻，还会摸雪，呲雪墙，耍酷耍得停不下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191585\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0bec8878&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOppwbsrzv15BcXqTYY8R3kjvfF37mEPFGgP6TliayQ8VrYrWU6vF2huw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">玩滑板速降，效果几乎可以媲美《白日梦想家》原片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191586\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d85434c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOibic0dkaic2ib0Orom3yUm3faAWR5MOgqrVPeeQ94KP5Ynxtw48V6tTV1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打篮球，投篮已经是小case了，直接给你来场篮球赛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191587\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4de55fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOXTuJw6ckRqMFSy6icgvgsEYY1ZlShSCtFN7XEGuzwibTmwH3BSyJucFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"