if%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOdiaiaeZVhcg5zMg6eOcibj5Hh9RSibDFhiboib2wakOUos6ek7FFXbgmp7FQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">受了重伤的男人捂着自己的胸口，大口吸气，强撑着不让自己倒下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191606\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5598591549295775\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4743977b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOsq5kl5ayMMibZw50IttabuX8kgA857wCwibB05FX9gTYl2PBdYhGBIHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">古灵精怪的女孩看着摄像头灿烂一笑，却发现对面的人没有回应，有点失落地收起了自己的表情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191607\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5598591549295775\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c29e0b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrNACaxJbSwiaEjLmpPvLsQOFwYHFq52arEkqGmQoWfxPEW5XHKdpTBWFWN2IQc7JQIzB5otGuggibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">李白在白帝城得知了自己被赦免的喜讯，又哭又笑，喜极而泣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191635\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" da